document: Object-Oriented Programming: Classes, inheritance, polymorphism, and design principles.
Advanced Databases: Query optimization, distributed databases, and data warehousing.
Frontend Development: Modern JavaScript frameworks, UI/UX design, and responsive layouts.
Distributed Systems: Fault tolerance, consensus algorithms, and large-scale architectures.
DevOps Practices: CI/CD pipelines, container orchestration, and infrastructure automation.
Data Visualization: Interactive dashboards, storytelling with data, and visualization tools.
Network Fundamentals: IP addressing, switching, routing, and network troubleshooting.
Ethical Hacking: Vulnerability assessment, penetration testing, and social engineering.
Human-Computer Interaction: Interface evaluation, usability studies, and accessibility design.
Cloud Architecture: Serverless design, auto-scaling, and cost optimization strategies.
